    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/ff11babce52675dca406dcd5a7fbd008.poster.avif?t=1712844212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/ff11babce52675dca406dcd5a7fbd008.webm?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/ff11babce52675dca406dcd5a7fbd008.mp4?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take the journey of a lifetime with Thor and the Vikings! Go to Ancient Greece and help Thor, Hercules’ daughter Alexia, and the other warriors save Midgard from Fenrir. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/3922ad53984d6dc50b02f5b4fe0b0e56.poster.avif?t=1712844212\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/3922ad53984d6dc50b02f5b4fe0b0e56.webm?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/3922ad53984d6dc50b02f5b4fe0b0e56.mp4?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fenrir, a giant wolf, is ready to destroy Midgard and all its inhabitants in his rage. Follow Fenrir’s story and explore the source of his immense anger as he sets off on a path of destruction. Discover a thrilling story and find out what made Fenrir so angry that he has resolved to destroy Midgard.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/e47e0a654b2ff20751972845b2ae7aa5.poster.avif?t=1712844212\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/e47e0a654b2ff20751972845b2ae7aa5.webm?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/e47e0a654b2ff20751972845b2ae7aa5.mp4?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Are you ready to join the Vikings on their epic quest to defeat the Minotaur? You’ll have to prove your worth by solving the Gods’ puzzles. Embark on an unforgettable adventure as you join the Vikings in their mission to bring peace back to the world!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/e1cef6066b6f46210ea6da2b54f55ef1.poster.avif?t=1712844212\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/e1cef6066b6f46210ea6da2b54f55ef1.webm?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/e1cef6066b6f46210ea6da2b54f55ef1.mp4?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready to embark on a journey to the mythical world of Olympus! Go on Zeus’ quest and find a special flower for the goddess Calypso. Along the way, you will explore the mysterious underworld, meet Hades, and uncover secrets about Cerberus.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/8caefa860968e5941e9879ac4ca0912e.poster.avif?t=1712844212\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307690/extras/8caefa860968e5941e9879ac4ca0912e.webm?t=1712844212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st